<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sign-In Notification</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tsukimi+Rounded:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Tsukimi Rounded', sans-serif;
            color: #FFFFFF; 
            background-color: #14121D; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #14121D;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #C5FF20; 
            color: #201E28; 
            padding: 4px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Tsukimi Rounded', sans-serif;
        }
        .email-header img {
            max-width: 40px; 
            height: auto;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #FFFFFF; 
            font-family: 'Tsukimi Rounded', sans-serif;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #C5FF20; 
            color: #201E28; 
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: 'Tsukimi Rounded', sans-serif;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #C5FF20;
            color: #14121D;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Tsukimi Rounded', sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #EAD69F; 
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .email-body, .email-footer {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .email-header img {
                max-width: 80px; 
            }
            .button {
                width: 100%; 
                display: block;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="Iki_logo.png" alt="Iki App"> 
            <h1>Welcome back, {{firstName}}!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>We noticed a sign-in to your account at {{signInTime}} from {{device}}.</p>
            <p>If this was you, there's no need for further action.</p>
            <p>If you did not sign in, please secure your account immediately.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{securityLink}}" class="button">Click here to change your password</a>
            </div>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@ikiwellness.com">support@ikiwellness.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Ikiwellness. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

   